Strange Tiles can be found inside of the Hallowed Sepulchre. The tiles will randomly light up, while lit they will teleport any player that steps on them, players will be teleported forward if the tile is blue and backwards if the tile is yellow and will both make the player temporarily immune to attacks for a few seconds after teleporting.

'''Strange Tiles''' can be found inside of the [[Hallowed Sepulchre]]. The tiles will randomly light up, while lit they will teleport any player that steps on them, players will be teleported forward if the tile is blue and backwards if the tile is yellow and will both make the player temporarily immune to attacks for a few seconds after teleporting.
